l, with the majority speaking [[Finland-Swedish|Swedish]] ({{formatnum:{{pct|{{Infobox Finnish Municipality/native language Swedish|Kronoby}}|{{Infobox Finnish Municipality/native language total|Kronoby}}|1}}}}) and the minority [[Finnish language|Finnish]] ({{formatnum:{{pct|{{Infobox Finnish Municipality/native language Finnish|Kronoby}}|{{Infobox Finnish Municipality/native language total|Kronoby}}|1}}}}).<ref name=\"population by language\" />\n\n[[Kokkola-Pietarsaari Airport]] is located in Kronoby.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat-inline|Kronoby}}\n*[http://www.kronoby.fi/ Municipality of Kronoby] \u2013 Official website {{in lang|sv|fi}}\n\n{{ostrobothnia}}\n\n[[Category:Municipalities of Ostrobothnia (region)]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1607]]\n\n\n{{WesternFinland-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kronoby"}
